.png", "id": "745178276813183", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974825_745178280146516_8322056193690440371_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Su5wvY1LLjYQ7kNvgGU7D9i&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A6qVHJ62F4LLXjmqu-yPy9q&oh=00_AYDL3hqzSM7DENNiK87jfBjZlUZCUxMGHwANJ-LeGB6upw&oe=66E58B46"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Trailer_cover.png", "id": "582094933577973", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031495_582094936911306_6800017255329826407_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=MKxHZAGDI5kQ7kNvgH13UY5&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A6qVHJ62F4LLXjmqu-yPy9q&oh=00_AYAq0zbnlWm7OUJcArkOtFR_zZSGu2Jg1EZPkgeXuZR1zg&oe=66E559E3"}, "display_name": "Archery Land", "keywords": [], "long_description": "You became a warrior who was called by the goddess to protect the shrine of water. \nAs evening approaches, monsters aiming for the Shrine of Water appear.\n\nWarrior! \n\nPass 6 ordeals to protect the shrine of water from monsters.  And become a legendary warrior who protects the shrine of water and protects the goddess by killing monsters! \n\nAlso, Be the greatest warrior in a breathtaking 1v1 battle with other warriors in the arena of Archery Land.", "short_description": "Archery Land is a single, multiplayer VR shooting game, and Enjoy the thrilling feeling of hitting the target in our Archery Land by aiming the bow at the wide land.\n"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Cover-MiniLandscape.png", "id": "1094889764444935", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974655_1094889767778268_3491009783949024005_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4xriVD1MupMQ7kNvgHWqwEG&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A6qVHJ62F4LLXjmqu-yPy9q&oh=00_AYC1o6bufGwJaFfjhBWpqssMYE8ZUOVQcFFJmWjo4jDlvQ&oe=66E58EC1"}, {"file_name": "Logo.png", "id": "1038643100096859", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "